# 1. Ignore the CONTENTS of any data folder
**/data/*

# 2. But make an EXCEPTION for .txt files inside data folders
!**/data/*.txt

# 3. Block all .jsonl and .parquet files everywhere else
**/*.jsonl
**/*.parquet

# 4. Block python cache
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc

# 5. Block DBs and backups
**/*.sqlite
**/*.bak